data.description: Public:   Sellers set this home up to be their forever home. The layout of this .45 acres is incredible.  From the pool with a deck around it, to the beautifully landscaped courtyard, to the 30'X37' shop with an 11ft door.  All this with endless lighting all around the property, you will seriously have no reason to leave your home. In 2022 the sellers installed 18.4 KW Solar Panels, making the monthly power bills $15 per month, which is including a 10 year manufacturer warranty that is transferable to the new buyer.  Also in 2022 - New HVAC with an air purification (Halo), New gutters, Tankless hot water tank and a New roof.  Relax in the sunroom or go out to the back yard to enjoy the view of Roxy Ann Peak. RV parking with full hook-ups- 30 amps.  Let's not forget the studio/office! Great home for entertainment with a lot of parking. It's definitely a must see!
